<node ID="ID_43087695" CREATED="1553759019282" MODIFIED="1553759019282" LINK="https://www.energycentral.com/c/ec/us-now-leads-energy-waste"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px">The United States is among the most wasteful nations in the world when it comes to unused energy. 71% of energy expended in transportation</font></span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://www.energycentral.com/c/ec/us-now-leads-energy-waste" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: black; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="black" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="font-weight: 400">is lost as waste</span></font></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px">, 66% of electricity is wasted, and 20% of energy used in manufacturing is considered non-useful. As a nation and a world, we have a long way to go when it comes to utilizing more efficient ways of producing and consuming energy. These alternate solutions include but aren&#8217;t limited to renewables and</font></span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="https://www.nrg.com/business/all-products-and-services/demand-response.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: black; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="black" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="font-weight: 400">demand-response utility programs</span></font></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px">, which direct energy along a grid based on households&#8217; unique needs and use times. As of now, with electricity constantly flowing to all recipients at all times,</font></span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="http://www.erc-co.org/spooky-statistics-about-energy-and-water-waste/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: black; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="black" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="font-weight: 400">the U.S. is wasting 61% to 81% of the energy</span></font></a><span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">flowing through its grids. That waste ultimately totals $130 billion in energy that is being billed for and expended but is not being used. Creating more usage-determined, efficient ways of consuming energy is also in the interest of individuals, as</span><span>&#160;</span></font><a href="http://www.erc-co.org/spooky-statistics-about-energy-and-water-waste/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: black; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="black" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="font-weight: 400">household spending on utilities has climbed</span></font></a><span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Airbnb Cereal App Book" size="18px"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Airbnb Cereal App Book; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">by as much as 119% since 2001. One way to establish smarter systems of consumption is through the tokenization and trade of energy.</span></font>
  </body>
</html>

</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_208448112" CREATED="1553759028493" MODIFIED="1553759028493"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
